column1: NOTE 1: HCB-only samples are identified as 'HCB-SurfGrab' under CollMeth and were only analyzed for cyanobacteria

NOTE 2: All 'Phyto_Res_VanDorn' and 'Phyto_Res_Net' samples identified under CollMeth were analyzed for the entire phytoplankton assemblage (e.g., green algae, diatoms, cyanobacteria, cryptomonads, etc.)
NOTE 3: StationID's for 'Phyto_Res_VanDorn' and 'Phyto_Res_Net' samples correspond to StationIDs and associated chemical and physical data in the 'ChemPhysData_2002-2021' worksheet
NOTE 4: HCB-only samples identified as 'HCB-SurfGrab'  under CollMeth do not have associated chemical and physical data in the 'ChemPhysData_2002-2021' worksheet
